<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gesture-n">gesture <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dʒestʃə(r)/    美 /'dʒestʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>姿势；手势：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>gesture language
手势语；身势语</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He made a rude <strong>gesture</strong> at the driver of the other car.
他向另一辆车的司机做了一个不雅的手势。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>表示；姿态</strong></h4>
<p>sth that you do that shows others what you think or feel：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Handshake is a <strong>gesture of</strong> friendship.
握手是一种友好的表示。</p></div></div>